{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he opened this up, and he read me exact dates when I went over to the continent, what I did, where I was based.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, not on the front here, but where the headquarters were of the illegal immigration somewhere in Paris, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had everything there, exact dates and everything else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my heart was sinking lower and lower because, you know, I felt I'd wasted another 20 pounds--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the end, he took out his big stamp, and he banged this onto my application form.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he stood up, and he shook hands with me, and he said, fortunately, of course, our two countries are now at peace.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've got to remember that I put down on my present nationality, on my application form, of course, Israeli, of which I was immensely proud.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have to put German anymore or stateless.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I put down Israeli.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, he said, fortunately our two countries are at peace, and this is a good thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he also said-- I remember that-- he says I envy you for your experiences.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I doubt if I would have had the same drive or guts or whatever, he sort of said, had I been given that sort of opportunity.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so here I was, you see, of dual nationality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would just like to say this, that it is difficult to imagine any other country that could have been perhaps quite so-- so-- so-- so open minded in a situation of this nature.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After all, I never killed anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I never took up arms against Britain.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
